                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>2. Quality of Work</strong><br><span style="font-size:12px;color:#555;">Accuracy,
                                thoroughness, and neatness of work produced.</span></td>
                        <td class="rating-col"><%= autoRating %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>3. Productivity & Time Management</strong><br><span
                                style="font-size:12px;color:#555;">Ability to complete tasks within assigned
                                deadlines.</span></td>
